0xD29D8EDD// GetMapdataFromHashKey
int GET_MAPDATA_FROM_HASH_KEY(Hash mapdataHandle);Parameters:mapdataHandle: The input map data handle.Returns: A transient (non-persistable) index to the requested mapdata, or -1.Returns the transient map data index for a specified hash.
This function supports SDK infrastructure and is not intended to be used directly from your code.
